  "body": "# Issue\r\nWe are currently assigning `state.persistent_committees` as a shuffling of `ValidatorRecord`s rather than just `validator_indices`\r\n\r\n```python\r\npersistent_committees=split(shuffle(initial_validator_registry, ZERO_HASH), SHARD_COUNT)\r\n```\r\n\r\n# Proposed solution\r\nSomething like the following\r\n```python\r\npersistent_committees=split(\r\n    shuffle(\r\n        [validator_index for validator_index in range(len(initial_validator_registry))],\r\n        ZERO_HASH\r\n    ),\r\n    SHARD_COUNT\r\n)\r\n```",
